<h1>SekibanWasm Rust</h1>

<p>Rust WASM variant of the SekibanWasmRuntime internal usage sample.</p>
<p>This sample demonstrates Aspire + Rust WASM module + Blazor Web management UI.</p>

<ul>
    <li><strong>WASM Module</strong>: Rust compiled to WASI (src/wasm-projectors/rust)</li>
    <li><strong>API Service</strong>: .NET API with Wasmtime projection runtime (C#)</li>
    <li><strong>Rust Domain</strong>: src/wasm-projectors/rust/domain</li>
    <li><strong>Rust Client API</strong>: src/internalUsages/rust/SekibanWasm.Rust.ClientApi</li>
    <li><strong>Web UI</strong>: This Blazor application consuming the Rust Client API</li>
</ul>

<p>Navigate to <a href="/weather">Weather</a> to manage weather forecasts.</p>
